metadata.name: Street Of Dreams VIP
metadata.description: Cafes attract musicians, comedians, performers, poets, and many other forms of art. NFTs aim to make art digital, accessible, and provide realistic forms of distribution for artists. These artists often overlook the potential of NFTs to change their lives, but soon it will be easily accessible via your favorite cafe in real life and the metaverse! Purchase includes membership and privileges in the exclusive NFT Artist Cafe. Limited to 2,000
